FIELD.name: source_id
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Unique source identifier (unique within a particular Data Release)

FIELD.name: band
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Photometric band: G (per-transit combined SM-AF flux), BP and RP.

FIELD.name: time
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit averaged G band observing time

FIELD.name: mag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit averaged G band Vega magnitude

FIELD.name: flux_error
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit averaged G band flux error

FIELD.name: flux_over_error
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit averaged G band flux divided by its error

FIELD.name: rejected_by_photometry
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit unavailable or rejected by photometry processing.

FIELD.name: rejected_by_variability
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Average G transit photometry rejected by variability processing

FIELD.name: other_flags
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Additional processing flags with debugging information.
